            tag:"Vocab · Batch 1", tagClass:"tv", type:"vocab",
            desc:`SSC One Word Substitution — words 888 to 916. Har <b style="color:var(--v)">purple word</b> pe hover karo for meaning + example.`,
            note:`<b>📌 SSC Note:</b> Yeh saare words <b>SSC CGL/CHSL One Word Substitution</b> mein pooche ja chuke hain. Story padho, phir bina hover ke recall karo!`,
            recallTest:"Incognito · Indefatigable · Indelible · Incontrovertible · Inexorable · Infallible · Inextinguishable · Indispensable",
